<template><div><h1 id="準備步驟1-下載mcl" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#準備步驟1-下載mcl" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 準備步驟1-下載mcl</h1>
<h2 id="一鍵安裝版-建議" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#一鍵安裝版-建議" aria-hidden="true">#</a> <a href="https://github.com/iTXTech/mcl-installer" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">一鍵安裝版<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>(建議)</h2>
