<h2 id="無jdk版" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#無jdk版" aria-hidden="true">#</a> <a href="https://github.com/iTXTech/mirai-console-loader" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">無JDK版<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></h2>
